parameters:
Cotton: "Hehehe♪ I knew you'd be there~? You're so simple.
But you're not there... It's a trap♪"
\F[sirius_angry]Sirius: "Gah!!"

Cotton: "Hey Akane, there's a kind of pleasure you still
don't know about♪ It's more exciting than doing it outside,
more than in a bed... tight and dark places are thrilling♪"
\F[sirius_angry]Sirius: "That's because you're a pervert, Cotton!"
Cotton: "You can't lie about what feels good~♪"

Cotton: "That's right, I've already told your friends that
you're here♪ I wonder if you can escape~?"
Wata: "Wrong again~♪ Too bad~♪"

Wata: "Akane, don't you want to get close and personal with
someone you love? Inside a locker... it happens naturally,
you know♪"
\F[sirius_angry]Sirius: "You don't need a locker for that!"

Wata: "The 'naturally' part is what's important. I wonder if
you get that, Akane~?"

Wata: "Well, whatever! Of course, I've already told our
friends♪ Can you escape, I wonder~?"

Wata: "Why are you being so stubborn!? I don't
understand..."

\F[sirius_angry]Sirius: "I'm not being stubborn! I have my own way of
feeling good!!"
Wata: "What does that mean!? What is it?"
Wata: "I don't want to hide... I want to be more free...!!"
Wata: "I don't get it...!"

Wata: "Isn't this just a waste of effort? Give up already.
I'm protected by the love of my comrades!"
\F[sirius_angry]Sirius: "Love?"
Wata: "You'll never reach it... Everyone is protecting me!"

Wata: "Don't even think about getting close to my favorite
locker... my 'nest of love'... I won't allow it!"
\F[sirius_damage]Sirius: "Ugh!!"
hide_actor_hud
\F[sirius_damage]Sirius: "Guh!! Get off me!!"
